data.description: This beautiful house is well illuminated and well maintaned, with a private pool and jacuzzi and a peaceful covered porch, a perfect landscape in front and back.  Spacious title floor bedrooms, master suite with walk-in closet and double sink ensuite.  A gorgeous kitchen connected with family room, with a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, beautiful backsplash.  Living room with large windows, ceiling fans and title flooring.  All that, inside the Weston Hills gated community, with pools, park, playground and splash pad.  Nearby amusement parks.  Don´t miss this opportunity!!
